      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>Wait, $1.5 million? That doesn't sound right. I was looking at the preliminary internal audit earlier and it showed we were pretty much at zero, maybe even a small surplus in the hardware maintenance fund. Are you sure about that amount? Can you walk me through where that $1.5M is actually sitting?",
